</blockquote><br />\n玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a9a2c98124fe94b86710d8ea826299d2f5ad59","tid":60474,"uid":43436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n預到咁炆先整台証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你尋日講都可能仲有機，黎緊e幾日放假點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算啦經一事長一智，果日話自己病左算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f26d9ba0c7eff00f001969ccac946727494704","tid":60474,"uid":15796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇BNO呀<br />\n<br />\n有仲有得救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇用啦下話<br />\n二號先開門"},{"pid":"4ba870c1a9388039ec58eef1650dbc0bae2ef8f7","tid":60474,"uid":8016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n預到咁炆先整台証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你尋日講都可能仲有機，黎緊e幾日放假點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算啦經一事長一智，果日話自己病左算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0b9d9ece960e678bf129c4442ce8e165cd27b2","tid":60474,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係公幹/死左人依啲急事，齊晒所有證明文件最快都要兩三日先批，仲要睇個啊sir係咪好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家你得返半日，仲要係因為你大頭蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇情講架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留係香港啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4385050003c401b4373471f3665394f339e14fe2","tid":60474,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"搞證呢d不嬲係優先度最高 只好怪自己on9"},{"pid":"0c9092067c4bc8f9926db16e57ca862bc5250c6c","tid":60474,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"6個月未到期既回鄉證可以<br />\n台灣係中國既省份"},{"pid":"3de0408e43b980b724c5edd02e10bd6dee672f39","tid":60474,"uid":32112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"無BNO? 點做真香港人呀你"},{"pid":"4c87a01f61f49d403e604d441192f1e9d7053f7a","tid":60474,"uid":42534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"試下去灣仔 帶齊資料問啦<br />\n不過旅行原因一定唔俾<br />\n但既然巴打係跟學校 可能有非旅遊原因<br />\n<br />\n本來已經係台灣玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係冇半年"},{"pid":"54d914f1b7f0f84edcc632577288186fffeb4583","tid":60474,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"6560f486a5551a46ac00d3cd125db0e70c484bc2","tid":60474,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"1f831e700e625af296eea5a346a050864580856e","tid":60474,"uid":28622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇可能"},{"pid":"bb2a525e363ff6ad21c4c74cacff67acc054869b","tid":60474,"uid":8074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"雖然聽日離2號仲有半日辦公時間<br />\n當比你見到主任佢又好人批快比你<br />\n但你點要人半日內整起本passport比你呀屌你<br />\n定覺得政府工會放假同你返工呀<br />\n咪撚on9啦2號出發依家先整台證"},{"pid":"65af00c68a11bc07d78dbf46c20956a26f94ad84","tid":60474,"uid":24033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無BNO? 點做真香港人呀你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有BNO就真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個乜撚野定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申有"},{"pid":"e3bf409416df9c933728effeebc266bf28333846","tid":60474,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6個月未到期既回鄉證可以<br />\n台灣係中國既省份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明朝的劍斬清朝的官.jpg"},{"pid":"d9090f93693e0ecce06842490d0383c580a2ce7d","tid":60474,"uid":59888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"認真答 好似可以落地簽<br />\nbtw,立即感受到BNO有幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前買哂野臨出發先發現BNO過期,一日拎到緊急，不過好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653a0c13e840e0b22bfee2e934da290787d3659f","tid":60474,"uid":15796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答 好似可以落地簽<br />\nbtw,立即感受到BNO有幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前買哂野臨出發先發現BNO過期,一日拎到緊急，不過好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我簽你老母咩<br />\n機都上唔到落乜撚野地<br />\n屌唔識野咪衝出嚟柒<br />\n認真喎 返去玩玩具啦"},{"pid":"e293bf4b78e06b4d864ac4021d9132b084c295e0","tid":60474,"uid":5708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"無睇清楚原來入台證要個護照有六個月有效期<br />\n<br />\n係去親邊度都要有6個月有效期"},{"pid":"8d08841d9c92bee6790875be109c2490afe96009","tid":60474,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"留係學校啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ca9d86c5e274f2798d3c9c115f645289f8f2b0","tid":60474,"uid":15796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無睇清楚原來入台證要個護照有六個月有效期<br />\n<br />\n係去親邊度都要有6個月有效期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本唔洗"},{"pid":"67a2d1f5eb142aad525ece2fcafff7bc76b759c3","tid":60474,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:15:39.000Z","msg":"2009-01-15 22:12:57 補充： <br />\n最後真係去唔到台灣&hellip;護照差一日香港0個邊都唔會批台證畀你&hellip;亦都唔畀你出境，唔會有任何辦法，包括坊間謠傳的有台灣公司出信你去都係唔得，因為台灣哪邊特別麻煩。如果係去日本，護照不足六個月有效期反而都可以去到，以前泰國都得，但近年已收窄制度唔批準，大家請留意！"},{"pid":"f7b3ec32bc9d81c9ffcbe6b1322fd8fe21410242","tid":60474,"uid":59888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真答 好似可以落地簽<br />\nbtw,立即感受到BNO有幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj